  ('federal-onecard', 'federal-onecard', 'Federal Bank', 'OneCard', 'Visa', 'high', 'mid_tier', 'retail', 0, 0, NULL, 1, 3.75, 45.0, '2.5% of amount withdrawn or Rs. 500 whichever is higher (Not applicable for Wave Credit Card)', 'All cash advances carry finance charges equal to the charges on revolving credit (Interest on Revolving Credit / APR, ranging from 23.88% i.e. 1.99% per month to 45.00% i.e. 3.75% per month based on Average Monthly Balance for last Quarter) from the date of withdrawal until paid. For cash advances, interest is charged from the date of the transaction until the date of payment; there is no interest free period for cash advances.', 'Total Amount Due Rs. 0-250: Rs. 0; Rs. 251-1000: Rs. 250; Rs. 1001-5000: Rs. 500; Rs. 5001-25000: Rs. 1,000; Rs. 25001 & above: Rs. 1,250 (w.e.f. 20th August 2024)', '5X reward points on the top-2 monthly spend categories; points credited instantly and never expire', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['5X reward points on the top-2 monthly spend categories; points credited instantly and never expire']::text[], 'metal card', 'https://www.getonecard.app/', 'https://www.federal.bank.in/credit-cards-mitc', 'Federal x OneCard co-brand MITC (OneCard MITC.pdf): issued by Federal Bank in partnership with FPL Technologies (NOT the CSB variant); annual/joining Nil (getonecard.app); forex 1% (getonecard.app blog). Finance inherits Federal issuer default (3.75%/mo, 45% p.a.) - OneCard''s own rate is app/profile-determined and not published -> needs_review. type=cobrand. See sources.json id ''federal-onecard''.', 'matched', DATE '2026-07-01', 'needs_review', true),
